The problem that we test here is if there is an attempt to forward from
a collocated location to a remote one then object's stub becomes partially
collocated and partially remote.

Successful output:

$>./run_test.pl
Starting Server
Starting Other Server
OK, now try to resolve a co-located IORTable entry...
IN LOCATOR!  Forwarding client to: IOR:
We narrowed the object, now let's invoke it!
Server - event loop finished
Leaving task!
